These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, almond-milk
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | mirinda |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  bartender, scientist
1. the bartender is on the left or right of the scientist##3
2. the scientist is on the right of the bartender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Job   | bartender | scientist |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, collecting
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | collecting | baking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: funk, indie
1. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of funk##1
2. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |
| Music-Genre   | indie | funk |

